.index set-debug-level
.usage builtin-function
.syntax
(set-debug-level number)

.description
Debug level 0 provides no extra diagnostic information after an exception. 
Debug level 1 provides a lisp function call stack.
Debug level 2 provides lexical and dynamic variable stack.
`$debugging` is set to false for levels 0/1 and true for level 2.

.see-also
.api
$debugging



